Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:30.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们必须找到橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}We need to track down Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们找到了她的逃生舱\N{\fnArial\fs48}We found her pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们知道她就在地球上\N{\fnArial\fs48}We know she's out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:35.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她来这里是因为有工作\N{\fnArial\fs48}She came to earth with a job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且很可能她还会试着完成\N{\fnArial\fs48}and odds are she's still gonna try to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:39.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是我将大家聚集到这里的原因\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's why I've gathered you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我以为是你为了能帮我把衣服都叠了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I thought it was so you could help me fold all this laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:44.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊，当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm, that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:47.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的家务轮的点子很快就失效了\N{\fnArial\fs48}The chore wheel idea you had fell apart fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:49.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是我干的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是很乐于做这些事\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just really enjoy doing all of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们最好一起做\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's better if we do them {\i1}together.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}人类应该不穿衣服\N{\fnArial\fs48}Humans should just stop wearing clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这会有趣很多\N{\fnArial\fs48}It'd be a lot funnier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是个有教养的半人，不谢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm a civilified part-human, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:10.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}衣服是必需品\N{\fnArial\fs48}Clothing is a must.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.74,0:01:12.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:13.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有点多啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}This {\i1}is{\i} a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我打赌如果红宝石和蓝宝石在的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}I bet this folding would go faster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:18.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}叠起来一定会更快的\N{\fnArial\fs48}if Ruby and Sapphire were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我肯定她们会乐于见到你，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sure they'd be glad to see you, Steven,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:24.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不会为了衣物解体的\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I am not unfusing for laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗷\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:26.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，你不认为\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, you don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:29.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石会来找我们吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot would come looking for us, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:30.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不是她的首要目标\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}We{\i} weren't her priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:33.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她被派来完成幼儿园的工作\N{\fnArial\fs48}She was sent here to do something in the kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你觉得她还会尝试重启幼儿园？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you think she's still going to try to reactivate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:37.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:40.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果她重启成功了，注射器会重新工作的\N{\fnArial\fs48}If she gets it up and running, the injectors will turn back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}注...射器？\N{\fnArial\fs48}In...Jectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:43.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那...那是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}W-what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:45.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你已经看到过了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You've already seen them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者，你看到的是停用的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, you've seen them disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.28,0:01:49.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果橄榄石重新启动了注射器\N{\fnArial\fs48}If Peridot reactivates them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们会继续工作\N{\fnArial\fs48}they'll pick right up where they left off --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在地壳中种下宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}planting gems in the crust of the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:55.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在那里他们会慢慢孵化\N{\fnArial\fs48}where they'll incubate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:57.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并从地表吸光生命\N{\fnArial\fs48}and suck the life right out of the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:02:00.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不能让橄榄石重启这里的宝石人生产\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can't let Peridot restart gem production here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:04.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果失败了，整个星球会变成\N{\fnArial\fs48}If we do, the entire planet will become...
