Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:09.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！用词不错嘛！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!  That mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:13.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不用担心。我们会阻止她\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry. We'll stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来吧，水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, crystal gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:17.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}马上\N{\fnArial\fs48}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:21.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃。只要我们不用叠东西\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. As long as we don't have to fold anything.
