Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来啊。显然也有你，对不对？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on. That means you, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:31.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}毕竟你也是一个有教养的半宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a civilified part-gem, too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，你确定我们可以带上史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, are you sure we should bring Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这可能比较危险\N{\fnArial\fs48}This might be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们完全可以对付橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot's got nothing we can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，看起来没有启动的痕迹\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, nothing {\i1}looks{\i} activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}实际上，没有东西看起来被修复过\N{\fnArial\fs48}In fact, it doesn't look like anything's budged
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}离上次来都这么长时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}since the last time we were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:56.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你说的对\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但只是因为橄榄石还没来这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}But just because Peridot hasn't been here yet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不意味着她不会来\N{\fnArial\fs48}doesn't mean she won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:01.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:03.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们来对场地做个仔细的检查\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's do a thorough check of the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:06.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这样，我们能监视任何将来进入的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm-hmm. That way, we can monitor any future entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我觉得不错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm. Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm, mmm, mm, mmm, mm, mmm,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:16.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}mm, mmm, mm, mmm, mm, mmm, mm, mmm, mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:25.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}记录日期 陆 贰 伍。我是橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Log date 652. This is Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:29.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}更新状态——仍在被困在这可悲的星球上\N{\fnArial\fs48}Updating status -- still stuck on miserable planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:32.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合实验的进展十分顺利\N{\fnArial\fs48}The fusion experiments are developing properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一少部分实验品已经提前孵化——\N{\fnArial\fs48}A few have even emerged early --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呀～哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}eugggh! Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其他人和你在一起吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are the other ones with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然。怎么会不呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course. Why not?
