Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿！我做不了这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey! I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:08.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她也别想！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Neither can she!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！歪了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha! Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:20.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你觉得她受伤了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you think she's hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并没有\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:36.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔！鞭子变烫了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoooooa! Hot whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们这群水晶草包！来啊！互相伤害啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You crystal clods! Go ahead! Wreck this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:43.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看我在不在乎！我已经得到我要的了\N{\fnArial\fs48}See if I care. I already got what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}回来！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我要给她点颜色瞧瞧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm gonna bop her good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也要！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快点，石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hurry, Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果橄榄石的任务是重启幼儿园，\N{\fnArial\fs48}If Peridot's mission was to reactivate the kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}注射器应该已经开启了\N{\fnArial\fs48}the injectors would be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们并没有\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们来看看她到底在干什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's see what she was {\i1}actually{\i} doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在下面\N{\fnArial\fs48}Down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:25.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真是法师战士双修二合一啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're brains {\i1}and{\i} brawn -- the whole package.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}多谢啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是因为你是融合体吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is it 'cause you're a fusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我总得有点不能说的秘密吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I have to keep {\i1}some{\i} of my secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，求求你了！我想知道！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, please? I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你战士的能力来自红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is the strong part of you Ruby
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}法师的能力来自蓝宝石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}and the wise part of you Sapphire?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}两个都有\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's all of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当两个宝石人结合时\N{\fnArial\fs48}When two gems combine,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:43.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}会产生1+1>2的效果\N{\fnArial\fs48}it creates something greater than the sum of their parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是我如此炫酷掉渣天的原因\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's why I'm so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一直保持合体的感觉——\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's it like to stay fused all the --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不知为何，这里感觉更瘆人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know how, but this place is even creepier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}相比我们上次来的时候\N{\fnArial\fs48}than the last time we were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:00.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对。显然有什么秘密\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes. There's something going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}电源没有恢复\N{\fnArial\fs48}The power's not on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:04.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石当时在做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was Peridot doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看起来她从墙里把这些拉了出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}It looks like she pulled these out of the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有事情不对\N{\fnArial\fs48}Something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:16.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里...不止我们吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is there... Something in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:52.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看起来像两块宝石碎片拼在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}It looks like two gem shards stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}恶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其它的都这样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that what all these things are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石...拼到一起？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gems...Stuck together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:03.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:04.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mnh-mnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们该怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}求求你！说句话啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please! Talk to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Unh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这些是被打碎的水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}These were crystal gems shattered into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:53.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们被埋在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}They were buried together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么不动了？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why aren't you moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们被强制在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}They were forced together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:58.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们被强制融合\N{\fnArial\fs48}They were forced to fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:07:59.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不对\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我-我对不起\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！不，石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No! No, Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你快解体了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're coming undone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:08.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}求求你！到底怎么了？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Please! What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这一点也不像你！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This isn't like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们做到了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:41.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以，这就是母世界看待融合体的态度\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, this is what homeworld thinks of fusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们当时不可能知道她们会这么做\N{\fnArial\fs48}We couldn't have known they would do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们原来在这里——所有我们找不到的人\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is where they've been -- all the ones we couldn't find.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们一直都是这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}They've been here the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}玫瑰不可能知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose couldn't have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:50.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是对叛乱的惩罚！这不是我们的错！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This was punishment for the rebellion! It's not our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史-史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}S-Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:58.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们回来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，我们跟丢了橄榄石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, we lost Peridot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她的手指对我们来说太快了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Her fingers were too fast for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...这些是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um... What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}把它们放下！——什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Put them down! What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们需要将它们打回原形并用泡泡包起来\N{\fnArial\fs48}We need to poof and bubble all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.56,0:09:16.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不能让任何物体离开这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can't let any escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦。嘿，石榴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Hey, Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感觉怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还是很不好\N{\fnArial\fs48}Still damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦。好吧——衣服\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh. Right -- the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}里面有毛巾\N{\fnArial\fs48}There {\i1}are{\i} towels in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们在这有水泵吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do we even have plumbing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是怎么让洗衣机和甩干机工作的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do you get the washer and dryer to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:40.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}魔法\N{\fnArial\fs48}Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还...好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you...All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我希望你没看见那些\N{\fnArial\fs48}I wish you hadn't seen that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:51.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这没什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这很重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's {\i1}not{\i} okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为-为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}W-why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}母世界所做的——\N{\fnArial\fs48}What homeworld did --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}将消逝的宝石碎片\N{\fnArial\fs48}taking the shattered parts of fallen gems
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}拼接到一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}and combining them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并没有得到那些宝石人的同意\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those gems weren't asked permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}融合是自己的选择\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fusion is a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那些宝石人没有选择的余地\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those gems weren't given a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这不对！这不是融合！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It isn't right! It isn't fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:19.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是一种什么感受，作为一个融合体？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's it like, being a fusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你融合过\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}You've{\i} fused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我指，就像，无时无刻\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, like, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们还记得原来的自己吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you forget who you used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你只会忘记你曾经的孤独\N{\fnArial\fs48}You forget you were ever alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你看，当你融合时，你不会感觉像两个人\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know, when you fuse, you don't feel like two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你感觉像是一个个体\N{\fnArial\fs48}You feel like one being.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且原来的你\N{\fnArial\fs48}And your old names might as well be names
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}感觉就像是左手和右手\N{\fnArial\fs48}for your left arm and your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当你解体时，你是消失了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}When you split up, is it like you disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的存在体现的是我的——\N{\fnArial\fs48}I embody my --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我指，红宝石和蓝宝石的爱\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, Ruby and Sapphire's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我永远存在于她们之中，即使我解体了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll always exist in them, even if I split apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是那种爱的力量让我一直在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the strength of that love keeps me together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:55.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以我作为石榴可以保持非常长的时间\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I can stay Garnet for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是你如此出色的原因！——哦，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's why you're so great.Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不想拆开一对\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't want to break up a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是，你说的对\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}它们属于一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}They belong together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我可以做到\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ If I could begin to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你对我期望的一半\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ half of what you think of me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我愿意做任何事\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I could do about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:26.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我愿学会像你一样，去爱\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I could even learn how to love like you ♪
